style Autoconf is
written by "Akim Demaille <akim@freefriends.org>"
version is 1.1
requires a2ps 4.12i

documentation is
  "Suitable for both code(configure.in)code and library code(m4)code files."
end documentation

ancestors are
  sh
end ancestors

sequences are
  "dnl" Keyword Comment
end sequences

keywords in Keyword_strong are
  /\\b_?A[CM]_[A-Za-z0-9_]*/
end keywords

# It is fairly common in Autoconf to have strings like
#  Define if your system supports `foo'
operators are
  /`[^"`']+'/ Plain
end operators

end style
